query:
SELECT 
  county,
  address,
  saleDate,
  saleStatus,
  upsetBidCloseDate,
  openingBid,
  currentBid
FROM properties 
WHERE sourceType = 'hutchens' 
  AND upsetBidCloseDate IS NOT NULL
LIMIT 10
